    "category": "Text",
    "text": "+ Parabol $(P)$: $y = f(x)$ có định là điểm $M(-8;0)$ nên $f(x) = k(x+8)^2, (k \\neq 0)$."
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      162,
      185,
      984,
      261
    ],
    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\nH(-3; a) \\in (P) \\text{ nên } 25k = a \\Leftrightarrow k = \\frac{a}{25} \\Rightarrow f(x) = \\frac{a}{25}(x+8)^2.\n$$"
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      155,
      285,
      1574,
      415
    ],
    "category": "Text",
    "text": "+ Đường cong $(C)$: $y = g(x)$ là hàm bậc ba có ba nghiệm $x = \\pm 2; x = 8$ nên $g(x) = h(x^2 - 4)(x - 8), (h \\neq 0)$."
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      162,
      446,
      724,
      522
    ],
    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\nH(-3; a) \\in (C) \\text{ nên } -55h = a \\Leftrightarrow h = -\\frac{a}{55}\n$$"
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      162,
      553,
      927,
      628
    ],
    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\n\\Rightarrow g(x) = -\\frac{a}{55}(x^2 - 4)(x - 8) = -\\frac{a}{55}(x^3 - 8x^2 - 4x + 32).\n$$"
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      155,
      651,
      1288,
      749
    ],
    "category": "Text",
    "text": "+ Dựa vào đồ thị, ta có: $S_1 = \\int_{-3}^{-2} g(x)dx; S_3 = \\int_{2}^{8} g(x)dx; S_2 = -\\int_{-2}^{2} g(x)dx; S_4 = \\int_{-8}^{-3} f(x)dx$"
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      155,
      774,
      1210,
      872
    ],
    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\n+ S_1 + S_3 = S_2 + S_4 + \\frac{109}{12} \\Leftrightarrow \\int_{-3}^{-2} g(x)dx + \\int_{2}^{8} g(x)dx = -\\int_{-2}^{2} g(x)dx + \\int_{-8}^{-3} f(x)dx + \\frac{109}{12}\n$$"
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      162,
      897,
      870,
      995
    ],
    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\n\\Leftrightarrow \\int_{-3}^{-2} g(x)dx + \\int_{-2}^{2} g(x)dx + \\int_{2}^{8} g(x)dx = \\int_{-8}^{-3} f(x)dx + \\frac{109}{12}\n$$"
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      162,
      1020,
      569,
      1117
    ],
    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\n\\Leftrightarrow \\int_{-3}^{8} g(x)dx = \\int_{-8}^{-3} f(x)dx + \\frac{109}{12}\n$$"
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      162,
      1142,
      895,
      1238
    ],
    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\n\\Leftrightarrow \\int_{-3}^{8} -\\frac{a}{55}(x^3 - 8x^2 - 4x + 32)dx = \\int_{-8}^{-3} \\frac{a}{25}(x+8)^2dx + \\frac{109}{12}\n$$"
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      162,
      1265,
      580,
      1348
    ],
    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\n\\Leftrightarrow \\frac{209}{60}a = \\frac{5}{3}a + \\frac{109}{12} \\Leftrightarrow a = 5.\n$$"
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      155,
      1373,
      679,
      1452
    ],
    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\n\\text{Suy ra } g(x) = -\\frac{1}{11}(x^3 - 8x^2 - 4x + 32)\n$$"
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      162,
      1475,
      814,
      1667
    ],
    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\ng'(x) = -\\frac{1}{11}(3x^2 - 16x - 4) = 0 \\Leftrightarrow \\begin{cases} x = \\frac{8+2\\sqrt{19}}{3} \\\\ x = \\frac{8-2\\sqrt{19}}{3} \\end{cases}\n$$"
  },
  {
